@{
ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
Layout = "_Layout";
}

<section class="h-full bg-[#FFF6E5]" style="margin-top: 75px; padding: 5% 10%;">
    <div class="relative w-full h-full text-center">
        <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">At Quick Bite, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our food delivery services.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Personal Information: Name, email address, phone number, delivery address, and payment details.</li>
            <li>Account Information: Username, password, and order history.</li>
            <li>Usage Information: Browsing activity, search queries, and interactions with restaurant partners.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use your data for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>To process and deliver your orders.</li>
            <li>To communicate with you regarding your account and orders.</li>
            <li>To improve our services and personalize your user experience.</li>
            <li>To comply with legal requirements and protect against fraud.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We implement security measures to protect your information. All passwords and payment data are encrypted to prevent unauthorized access. Please note that no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. You may also request the restriction of data processing or object to certain uses of your data by contacting us directly.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Quick Bite may share your information with third-party services such as payment processors and map software providers. These third parties are required to protect your data and may only use it for the specific services they provide.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Our website uses cookies to enhance your experience, including remembering your preferences and providing personalized content. You can control your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and users will be notified of significant updates.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact us at <a style="text-decoration: underline;" href="mailto:support@quick-bite.ca">support@quick-bite.ca</a>.</p>
    </div>
</section>